GrimLock looked down. "I... Was King of the Dino-Bots... Prime asked me to be 
a guardian, and with me my fellows, but the traitor Scourge attacked us, he 
nearly destroyed the others... He Killed Mirage..., and he placed me in a 
position where if my young friend here had not rebuilt me in this new form I would 
have faced a system crash... Scourge had my mind upgraded... and now not only 
do I know I failed, but he has taken Slag, Sludge, swoop, and snarl."

--part1_27.41f9ab86.2c181057_boundary
